synopsis: The government is asking Eiffel to design something spectacular for the 1889 Paris World Fair, but Eiffel simply wants to design the subway. Suddenly, everything changes when Eiffel crosses paths with a mysterious woman from his past.
tagline: You will never look at it the same way again.

synopsis: On an empty beach, 5 kids talk and talk, over the beach lenght. They are young but not dumb. Mean but not beamed. And cute but not stupid.

titre: Un Cuento De Amor (La Verdad Que Nadie Cuenta Pero Todos Conocen)
synopsis: Renata and Gabriel, a young couple of actors, arrives to their apartment ready to have a night of pleasure, until she finds an used condom that makes all their relationship's secrets emerge.
tagline: EVERYBODY KNOWS WHAT HAPPENS BETWEEN THIS WALLS

synopsis: Back in 1977, Dillon filmed Hillary and crew (including son Peter Hillary) as they jet boated from the mouth of the Ganges to the base of the Himalayas, then set out to climb peak Akash Parbat. Dillon has remastered existing and unseen footage, and interviewed crew members about Hillary's last big expedition.
tagline: How far can an adventure really go?
casting: ['Edmund Hillary', 'Peter Hillary', 'Graeme Dingle', 'Murray Jones', 'Mohan Kohli', 'Waka Attewell', 'Michael Dillon']
